content: I purchased this last year on my 2015 NVIDIA SHIELD. My family loved to play it. I upgraded to the new Shield over Christmas to find out this app is not compatible with the current model (2019 NVIDIA SHIELD). Please update this app!!! it's a 5 star app if I can play it... 1 star until then.
On my update on the shield tv it specifically said this game was newly accessible though after I purchased it, it says not compatible with shield tv. If this gets fixed I will redo my rating.
